file.name: LocalReferenceResolving.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  title: 'test'
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /entity/{id}:
    get:
      summary: 'Get entity'
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/id'
      responses:
        200:
          $ref: '#/components/responses/getEntity'

components:
  parameters:
    id:
      name: id
      in: path
      required: true
      schema:
        $ref: '#/components/schemas/id'
  responses:
    getEntity:
      description: 'Returns entity in JSON'
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/entity'
  schemas:
    entity:
      type: object
      required:
        - id
        - tags
      properties:
        id:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/id'
        tags:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/tags'
    id:
      type: integer
      minimum: 0
      maximum: 65535
    tags:
      type: array
      minItems: 1
      maxItems: 1
      items:
        $ref: '#/components/schemas/tag'
    tag:
      type: string
      enum:
        - tag
